Package atg.sitemap

Interface Summary
SitemapGenerator Interface for sitemap generators.
 

Class Summary
DynamicSitemapGenerator Sitemap generator service for dynamic items.
SitemapGeneratorService This service is responsible for sitemap and siteindex generation.
SitemapIndexGenerator Generates Sitemap index repository item which contains links to all sitemap entries.
SitemapPropertiesManager Utility class provides properties names for the Sitemap repository.
SitemapTools Utility methods for sitemap and siteindex items handling.
SitemapWriterService This service creates copies of sitemap and siteindex files to the local file system.
StaticSitemapGenerator Sitemap generator service that generates sitemap repository items in SitemapRepository for static pages.
